      <div
        class="flex items-start justify-center flex-col text-2xl leading-relaxed"
      >
        <p class="">
          <span class="">Ata Ahi Fitness</span> is an inclusive gym located in the
          heart of <span class="font-bold">Auckland</span> on Beach Road in the CBD.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
